related_questions.question: Do airlines prefer hard or soft luggage?
related_questions.snippet: Hard-sided bags protect fragile items better than soft bags and are easier to clean when necessary. Whether you opt for a hard-sided suitcase or a soft one, be sure that you're paying for good quality.
